  "description": "A vibrant coastal scene featuring powerful waves breaking towards a rocky shoreline. The foreground is filled with foamy white waves, transitioning into deeper turquoise and blue hues as the waves approach the distant landmass. A lone surfer is visible riding a wave in the middle ground. The background consists of dramatic, dark grey and brown cliffs and headlands, partially shrouded in mist. The sky is a clear, light blue, providing a striking contrast to the darker tones of the land and sea. The composition emphasizes the scale of the ocean and the rugged beauty of the coastline.",
